nt of 50-60 (ok, so I am 46 and the lowest in the zone by 3 levels), moderately equipped (none had epics or any NToV items), should have no problems. Some of the Xi mobs are clerics, some are SK, you will know by thier pet or their casting smite on you (or CHealing themselves).<br><br>If you have some player with you that has great tailoring skill (like 180+), only let them loot the shaded armor (no drop armor with no stats, along with mond worm hides are used to make WOW! tailored items, especially the tunic: AC 22, STR 10, STA 7, CHA 5, INT 8, HP 20, mana 20, all saves +5, all/all). <br><br>Potential problems are the worms. Triggered like traps, very high AC and some seem to have AoE manna drain (maybe it was my imagination, but I'm really sure one did that) <p><a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=64195'>Combat Profile</a><br><a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=64207'>Tradeskill Profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubarrandaam.showPublicProfile?language=EN>BarrandAam</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 290<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/1/02 10:33:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=357.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.health-tracker.com/pics/barr_new.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grodan's Cloak</span><hr size=1> Xi Thal<br><br>harmony or root = /yawn<br><br><br>paladin/shaman<br><br>paladin/druid<br><br>ect<br><br>have 0 problems killing him<br><br>Hard part is continually killing his ph over and over :P <p>-The Barr<BR><BR><b><a target="new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=77387